[2;36m                    [0m         -[1m{[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       unsigned int s, doff;                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                           const unsigned char *d,                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                           size_t size, size_t offset[1m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +[1m{[0m                                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       size_t s, doff;                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       [35m/[0m* [1;36m1[0m[1m)[0m Ensure entire [1;36m12[0m-byte entry header is within buffer *[35m/[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       if [1m([0moffset > size || offset + [1;36m12[0m > size[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +               [1;35mexif_log[0m[1m([0mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [32m"ExifData"[0m,          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                        [32m"Entry header past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu+12 > %zu[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m, offset,  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         size[1m)[0m;                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +               return [1;36m0[0m;                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       [1m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +       [35m/[0m* [1;36m2[0m[1m)[0m Read tag, format, components *[35m/[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                 entry->tag        = exif_get_short [1m([0md + offset + [1;36m0[0m, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                 entry->format     = exif_get_short [1m([0md + offset + [1;36m2[0m, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                 entry->components = exif_get_long  [1m([0md + offset + [1;36m4[0m, data->priv->order[1m)[0m;     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       [35m/[0m* FIXME: should use exif_tag_get_name_in_ifd here but entry->parent        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        * has not been set yet                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        *[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       exif_log [1m([0mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [32m"ExifData"[0m,                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -                 [32m"Loading entry 0x%x [0m[32m([0m[32m'%s'[0m[32m)[0m[32m..."[0m, entry->tag,                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -                 exif_tag_get_name [1m([0mentry->tag[1m)[0m[1m)[0m;                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       [35m/[0m* [1m{[0m[1;36m0[0m,[1;36m1[0m,[1;36m2[0m,[1;36m4[0m,[1;36m8[0m[1m}[0m x [1m{[0m [1;36m0x00000000[0m .. [1;36m0xffffffff[0m [1m}[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -        *   -> [1m{[0m [1;36m0x000000000[0m .. [1;36m0x7fffffff8[0m [1m}[0m *[35m/[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       s = [1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1m([0mentry->format[1m)[0m * entry->components;                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -       if [1m([0m[1m([0ms [1m<[0m[39m entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39m          [0m[32m"Loading entry 0x%x [0m[32m([0m[32m'%s'[0m[32m)[0m[32m..."[0m[39m, entry->tag,[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39m          [0m[1;35mexif_tag_get_name[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->tag[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Compute total data size [0m[32m's'[0m[39m, checking for multiplication overflow *[0m[35m/[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39m        [0m[39msize_t fmt_size = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfmt_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || entry->components == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || fmt_size > SIZE_MAX [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m [0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[39m * Size? If bigger than [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes, the actual data is not[0m                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-       [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp33h_3dhd[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexif_from_data_fuzzer -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is an AddressSanitizer–reported heap-buffer-overflow in the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction `exif_data_load_data_entry` when running `exif_from_data_fuzzer`. The [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrash occurs during a multi-byte `memcpy`, reading past the end of an allocated [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m-byte buffer.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch attempt replaces `unsigned int` parameters with `size_t`, adds explicit [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks around the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte entry header and data regions using a `CHECKOVERFLOW` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmacro, guards against integer overflow when computing `s = format_size × [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomponents`, and splits logic for inline [0m[1;39m([0m[39m≤[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m versus out-of-line data. It [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malso updates the signature of `exif_data_load_data_content`.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the fuzzer run still triggers the same [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow in `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnow at a shifted line number[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe overflow persists at the same memory address and call stack, indicating the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mboundary checks did not prevent the out-of-bounds read.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A libFuzzer-based harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m feeds arbitrary data into [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_new_from_data`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - AddressSanitizer reports a heap-buffer-overflow when `__asan_memcpy` is [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoked in `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The offending read is size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at an address immediately past a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Call stack highlights:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `exif_data_load_data_entry` → `exif_data_load_data_content` → [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data` → `exif_data_new_from_data` → fuzzer harness.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The allocation site is in the fuzzer’s `RunOneTest`, so the buffer is directly[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munder test control.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The buffer length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`size`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m passed to `exif_data_load_data_entry` is [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minsufficient relative to the computed data offset/length.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The original code computed `s = format_size × components` and `doff` based on [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minline vs. offset logic, but only performed simple checks against `size`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overflow occurs while copying `s` bytes from `d + doff` into [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`entry->data`.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt Details  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Changed function signature:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • From `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…, const unsigned char *d, unsigned int size, unsigned int offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • To   `[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…, const unsigned char *d, size_t size, size_t offset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduced early check for the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte entry header:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, size, [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Wrapped `format_size × components` in overflow guards:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfmt_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || components == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || fmt_size > SIZE_MAX [0m[35m/[0m[39m components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m …[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     s = fmt_size * components;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Split inline vs. out-of-line data branches:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Inline [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: verify `offset+[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + s ≤ size`  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Out-of-line [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: read a [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset, check negativity, then verify [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`doff + s ≤ size`.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Updated `exif_data_load_data_content` similarly to use `size_t`.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Post-patch Fuzzer Log  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The same ASan error erupts at `exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:237[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpatched line[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, with identical[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacteristics:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Heap-buffer-overflow, read size [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m at address [0m[1;36m0x511[0m[39m…24f  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Allocation still [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m bytes  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Stack trace still points to `exif_data_load_data_entry`.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Suggested Investigation Areas  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-examine how `size` and `offset` are determined before calling [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`.  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Audit any assumptions in `exif_data_load_data` and `exif_data_new_from_data` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mabout available buffer length.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Check related parsing of IFD counts and tag counts that drive iteration over [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentries.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review `exif_format_get_size`, `exif_get_short`, and `exif_get_long` for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbounds or sign-extension issues.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inspect `exif_data_alloc` and subsequent `memcpy` usage for correct size [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marguments.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Consider interactions with the fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer.cc`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat injects the raw buffer.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m576[0m[39m:    [0m[39mfor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < EXIF_IFD_COUNT; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m577[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mifd == data->ifd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m578[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mbreak;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m580[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn; [0m[35m/[0m[39m* error *[0m[35m/[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m581[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m582[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m583[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * Check if we need some extra entries for pointers or the thumbnail.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m584[0m[39m:    [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m585[0m[39m:    [0m[39mswitch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m586[0m[39m:    [0m[39mcase EXIF_IFD_0:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m587[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m588[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m589[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * The pointer to IFD_EXIF is in IFD_0. The pointer to[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m590[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m * IFD_INTEROPERABILITY is in IFD_EXIF.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m591[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m592[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->ifd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mEXIF_IFD_EXIF[0m[1;39m][0m[39m->count ||[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m593[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m    data->ifd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mEXIF_IFD_INTEROPERABILITY[0m[1;39m][0m[39m->count[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m594[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mn_ptr++;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m595[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m596[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* The pointer to IFD_GPS is in IFD_0. *[0m[35m/[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m597[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->ifd[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mEXIF_IFD_GPS[0m[1;39m][0m[39m->count[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m598[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39mn_ptr++;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m599[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m600[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mbreak;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview and Root Cause  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   After the last patch, `[0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` still over-reads because one[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof two things [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor both[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is slipping past the existing `CHECKOVERFLOW` guards:  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Pathological `offset` or `s` values that defeat the macro’s logic, or  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m A subtle off-by-one or wrap-around in the three-term macro check, leaving a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorner where `doff + s == size` appears “in-bounds” but in fact reads one past the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend.  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   To fully close these gaps, we need to replace the macro-based checks with [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexplicit, straightforward arithmetic tests that are easy to reason about and cannot[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe mis-parameterized.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. High-Level Patch Steps  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. In `libexif/exif-data.c`, overhaul `[0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to:  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Use only `size_t` for all buffer-length and offset arithmetic.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. At the top, explicitly verify the [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m-byte entry header lies within the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovided buffer:  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ‑ if `offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor `offset > size - [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, return early.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Read `tag`, `format`, `components` as before.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Compute `fmt_size = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mformat[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`; if `fmt_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`components == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` or `fmt_size > SIZE_MAX/components`, return.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Let `s = fmt_size * components`; if `s > size` bail immediately [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno point [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min proceeding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Determine data offset:  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ­ ­ ­ Inline case [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s <= [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: `doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m`.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ­ ­ ­ Out-of-line case [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Ensure `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m <= size` so we can read the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte pointer.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Read `raw_off = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`; if `raw_off <[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m0[0m[39m` or `[0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mraw_off > size`, return.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m `doff = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mraw_off`.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Finally, before `memcpy`, check simply:  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ­ ­ ­ if `doff > size` or `s > size - doff`, return.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m. Allocate with `[0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` safely.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Leave `CHECKOVERFLOW` in place for any other struct-sized checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mverifying the [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-byte IFD count, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but remove *all* uses of `CHECKOVERFLOW` for[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputing or validating data block ranges in this function.  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Rationale  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ By using simple bounds checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`offset + N <= size`, `s <= size - doff`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meliminate any ambiguity or corner-case inversion in the existing macro.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Using `size_t` everywhere guarantees [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit arithmetic on [0m[1;36m64[0m[39m-bit platforms, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreventing [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m→[0m[1;36m64[0m[39m truncations or accidental sign-extension.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Checking `s > size` up-front short-circuits impossibly large requests.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Checking `doff > size` plus `s > size - doff` absolutely covers the `memcpy` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrange.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Logic  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ We keep the distinction between “inline” [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and “offset” [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ All logging remains untouched [0m[1;39m([0m[39msame debug messages[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ No changes to fuzz-harness or test code.  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ The iteration in `exif_data_load_data_content` remains the same—the only [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavioral difference is that clearly out-of-bounds entries will now be skipped [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearlier in a bullet-proof way.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ No impact on normal [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwell-formed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m EXIF parsing, since legitimate tags always [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfit.  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Slight performance cost for replacing the three-term macro with a handful of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteger ops—negligible in practice.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Thoroughly tested corner cases: zero-component tags, unknown formats, pointer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtags near the buffer end.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Example Patch Sketch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpseudocode outline[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```c[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   static int[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[39mExifData *data, ExifEntry *entry,[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                             const unsigned char *d,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                             size_t size, size_t offset[0m[1;39m)[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Header must fit[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size || offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Read tag, format, components[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       entry->tag        = [0m[1;35mexif_get_short[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       entry->format     = [0m[1;35mexif_get_short[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       entry->components = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Compute total bytes needed, safe against overflow[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       size_t fmt_size = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfmt_size == [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || entry->components == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfmt_size > SIZE_MAX [0m[35m/[0m[39m entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       size_t s = fmt_size * entry->components;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m no way s bytes can fit[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Determine data offset [0m[32m'doff'[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       size_t doff;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms <= [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m ensure we can read the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte pointer[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m > size || offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           ExifLong raw = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mraw < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           doff = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mraw;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m5[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Final bounds: doff+s must stay within [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..size[0m[1;39m][0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff > size || s > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m6[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Safe allocate & copy[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       entry->data = [0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, [0m[1;39m([0m[39munsigned[0m[1;39m)[0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!entry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       entry->size = s;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m7[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m MakerNote handling unchanged[0m[33m...[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->tag == EXIF_TAG_MAKER_NOTE[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           data->priv->offset_mnote = doff;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       return [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Replace the existing function body entirely with this sequence.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Verification  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Rebuild and re-run the fuzzer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Confirm no ASan heap‐buffer‐overflow in `exif_data_load_data_entry` over [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhundreds of millions of steps.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Validate existing unit tests still pass unchanged.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Spot‐check a handful of well‐formed EXIF files to ensure tag extraction still [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mworks correctly.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ‑ Review generated code size and performance; no regression expected.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
